一、常用句型套路

　　1. Although it is commonly (widely/generally) held(felt/accepted/agreed) that…, it is unlikely to be true that…

　　尽管大家普遍地(广泛地/通常地)认为(感觉/接受/同意)……，但事实上并非如此……

　　2. It is true that (True, /To be sure, /Admittedly,)…, but this is not to say (it is unlikely /it doesn’t follow/it doesn’t mean/it won’t be the case) that…

　　真实情况是/当然……，但是这并不等于说(不太可能/并不会/并不意味着/并非如此)……

　　3. It would be possible (natural/reasonable) to think (believe/take the view) that…, but it would be absurd (wrong) to claim (argue) that…

　　这么认为(相信/持这种观点)……是有可能(自然的/合理的)，但如果断言(坚决主张)……就是荒唐的(错误的)

　　4. There is absolutely (in fact) no (every) reason for us to believe (accept/resist/reject) that…

　　对于我们来说绝对(事实上)没有任何理由相信(接受/反对/拒绝)……

　　5. The danger (problem/fact/truth/point) is that…

　　危险的(问题/事实/真相/关键)是……

　　6. I believe that the title statement is valid because (of)…

　　我相信题目的这种说法是有充分根据的，因为……

　　7. I agree with the above statement because I believe that…

　　我同意上述观点，因为我相信……

　　8. Although I appreciate that…, I cannot agree with the title statement.

　　尽管我赞成……，但我并不同意题目中的说法。

　　9. Now it is commonly (widely/generally/increasingly) believed (thought /held/accepted/felt/recognized/acknowledged) that… But I wonder (doubt) whether…

　　现在，尽管大家普遍地(广泛地/通常地/越来越)相信(认为/支持/承认/感觉/意识到/接受)……，但我想知道(怀疑)……

　　10. The increase (change/failure/success) in…mainly (largely/partly) results from (arises from/is because of)…

　　这种在……方面的增长(变化/失败/成功)主要(很大程度上/部分地)因为(源于/因为)……

　　11. There are many (different/several/a number of/a variety of) causes (reasons) for this dramatic (marked/significant) growth (change/decline/increase) in… First, … Second, …Finally,…

　　有很多(不同的/几个/许多/各种各样的)理由(原因)导致在……方面强烈的(明显的/显著的)增长(变化/下降/增加)……第一，……第二，……最后，……

　　12. Another reason why I dispute the above statement is that…

　　我质疑上述观点的另一个原因是……

　　13. There are numerous reasons why…, and I shall here explore only a few of the most important ones.

　　有很多原因导致……，我在这里只想详细叙述最重要的几点。

　　二、议论文的常用套语

　　As is known to all, it is important to be/do …

　　众所周知，重要的是……

　　I think there are at least two reasons for …

　　我认为至少有两个原因……

　　For one thing,… For another , …

　　其中之一，另一个是……

　　Let’s take … for example …

　　我们以……为例……

　　From what I have mentioned above we can see that without … we cannot …

　　从上述我提到的可以看出如果缺少……我们就不能……

　　It is clear that,… plays an important part in …

　　很明显，……在……方面起着重要作用。

　　It is because … that …

　　因为……

　　Different people, however , have different opinions on this matter .Some people think that …

　　但是，不同人对待这个事情上有不同的看法。有些人认为……

　　Others argue that …

　　另一些人认为……

　　According to them, all of us should …

　　按照上述内容，我们全部都应当……

　　In their opinion, nobody can … without…

　　他们认为，如果没有……没有人可以……

　　Compared with …, … has a lot of advantages over …

　　与……相比，……比……有很多优势。

　　There is no doubt that …

　　毫无疑问

　　In short (In brief /In a word), I firmly support the view that …

　　简而言之(简要的说/一句话)，我坚定地支持……的观点。

　　So my conclusion is that …

　　所以，我的结论是……
